ygData.messageBody:
Where can a 34 ranger get good exp.? Loot is
secondary in my mind right now, just because a number of my
friends have absolutly out leveled me and I am looking
for the quickest, easiest way to level. I am looking
for a number of zones that would be beneficial. I
know it sounds kinda like a contradiciton but I do not
like to stay in one zone for 5 or 6 levels. I find
that boring and repititious.<br>Any and all help would
be appreciated!!<br><br>Vanadeer<br>34
Season<br>Terris-Thule
